descriptor.name: Milk Delights Face Wash - Fine Gramflour (Oily Skin)
descriptor.short_desc:
NIVEA Milk Delights with Fine Gramflour cleanses your skin deeply to remove excess oil. The milk acts as a natural cleanser, and the fine gramflour helps reduce stickiness, giving you healthy looking skin that lasts through the day.
Warning: Avoid eye contact
Benefits:

Fine gram flour is beneficial in removing the excess oil from the skin and keeps your skin oil-free for the whole day, in just one use
Milk helps in naturally cleansing the skin while making it smooth and soft
The face wash effectively reduces stickiness, leaving your skin looking plump and healthy

How to use:

Step 1 - Shake well before use Step 2- Moisten your face and neck Step 3 - Apply gently Step 4 - Rinse thoroughly with water

Special Ingredients:
Gramflour
Other Ingredients:
Aqua, Glycerin, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Acrylates Copolymer, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Phenoxyethanol, Mannitol, Ethylparaben, Methylparaben, Sodium Chloride, Microcrystalline Cellulose, Polyquaternium-7, Sodium Hydroxide, Carnitine, PEG-14M, Sine Adipe Lac, Sodium Lauryl Sulfate, Squalane, Sodium Benzoate, Algin, Linalool, Limonene, Citronellol, BHT, Perfume, CI 77891, CI 77492

descriptor.name: Milk Delights Face Wash - Rose (Sensitive Skin)
descriptor.short_desc:
Delight your skin with the goodness of milk and the gentle power of rosewater, in the new NIVEA Milk Delights Face Wash with Caring Rose. Milk gently cleanses the skin while rose soothes it, leaving your skin looking healthy.
Warning: Avoid eye contact
Benefits:

Rose is gentle on sensitive skin because of its soothing properties
Milk helps in naturally cleansing the skin while making it smooth and soft
Rose reduces redness and irritation without causing any itchiness

How to use:

Step 1 - Shake well before use Step 2 - Moisten your face and neck Step 3 - Apply gently

Rose
